text: Martin Stockinger (born 10 February 1984) is an Austrian cross-country skier. He competed in the men's sprint event at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Austria Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Upper Austria Category:People from Rohrbach District
